{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"tabs","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n    <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions\"><strong>Extensões do navegador</strong></a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Começando</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/What_are_WebExtensions\">O que são extensões</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Your_first_WebExtension\">Sua primeira extensão</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Your_second_WebExtension\">Sua segunda extensão</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Anatomy_of_a_WebExtension\">Anotomia de uma extensão</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Examples\">Extensões de exemplo</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/What_next_\">Qual o proximo?</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Conceitos</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Using_the_JavaScript_APIs\">Usando as APIs Javascript</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Content_scripts\">Scripts de conteúdo</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Match_patterns\">Padrões de correspondência</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Working_with_files\">Trabalhando com arquivos</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Internationalization\">Internacionalização</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Content_Security_Policy\">Política de Segurança de Conteúdo</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Native_messaging\">Menssagens nativas</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Differences_between_API_implementations\">Diferenças entre implementações de API</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Chrome_incompatibilities\">Incompatibilidades do Chrome</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Interface de usuário</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface\">Interface de usuário</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Browser_action\">Botão da barra de ferramentas</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Page_actions\">Botão da barra de endereços</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Sidebars\">Barras Laterais</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Context_menu_items\">Itens do menu de contexto</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Options_pages\">Página de opções</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Extension_pages\">Páginas de extensão</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Notifications\">Notificações</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Omnibox\">Sugestões da barra de endereço</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/devtools_panels\">Painéis de ferramentas do desenvolvedor</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Como</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Intercept_HTTP_requests\">Interceptar solicitações HTTP</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Modify_a_web_page\">Modificar uma página da web</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Safely_inserting_external_content_into_a_page\">Insira conteúdo externo</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Sharing_objects_with_page_scripts\">Compartilhe objetos com scripts da página</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Add_a_button_to_the_toolbar\">Adicionar um botão à barra de ferramentas</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Implement_a_settings_page\">Implementar uma página de configurações</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Working_with_the_Tabs_API\">Trabalhe com a API Tabs</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_the_Bookmarks_API\">Trabalhar com a API Bookmarks</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_the_Cookies_API\">Trabalhe com a API de Cookies</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_contextual_identities\">Trabalhe com identidades contextuais</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Interact_with_the_clipboard\">Interact with the clipboard</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Build_a_cross_browser_extension\">Crie uma extensão para vários navegadores</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Firefox_differentiators\">Diferenciadores do Firefox</a></summary>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details open=\"\">\n        <summary>APIs JavaScript</summary>\n        <ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Browser_support_for_JavaScript_APIs\">Browser support for JavaScript APIs</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/alarms\">alarms</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks\">bookmarks</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/browserAction\">browserAction</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/browserSettings\">browserSettings</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/browsingData\">browsingData</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/clipboard\">clipboard</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands\">commands</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/contentScripts\">contentScripts</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/contextualIdentities\">contextualIdentities</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/cookies\">cookies</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/menus\">menus</a></li><li class=\"webextension-api-sidebar\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs\">tabs</a><ol></ol></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/theme\">theme</a></li></ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n      <summary>Chaves Manifest</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json\">Introdução</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      <ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/permissions\">permissões</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/short_name\">short_name</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/web_accessible_resources\">web_accessible_resources</a></li></ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n     <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Workshop de extensões</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/develop/\">Desenvolver</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/publish/\">Publicar</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/manage/\">Gerenciar</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/enterprise/\">Empreendimento</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/Contact_us\"><strong>Contate-Nos</strong></a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Canais</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://blog.mozilla.org/addons\">Blog de complementos</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://discourse.mozilla.org/c/add-ons\">Fóruns complementares</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://chat.mozilla.org/#/room/%23addons:mozilla.org\">Add-ons chat</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Interact with the browser's tab system.</p>\n<p>You can use this API to get a list of opened tabs, filtered by various criteria, and to open, update, move, reload, and remove tabs. You can't directly access the content hosted by tabs using this API, but you can insert JavaScript and CSS into tabs using the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/executeScript\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.executeScript() (en-US)</a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/insertCSS\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.insertCSS() (en-US)</a> APIs.</p>\n<p>You can use most of this API without any special permission. However:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To access <code>Tab.url</code>, <code>Tab.title</code>, and <code>Tab.favIconUrl</code>, you need to have the <code>\"tabs\"</code> <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/permissions\">permission</a>.\n    <ul>\n      <li>In Firefox, this also means you need <code>\"tabs\"</code> to <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/query\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.query() (en-US)</a> by URL.</li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li>To use <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/executeScript\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.executeScript() (en-US)</a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/insertCSS\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.insertCSS() (en-US)</a>, you must have the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/permissions#host_permissions\">host permission</a> for the tab</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Alternatively, you can get these permissions temporarily, only for the currently active tab and only in response to an explicit user action, by asking for the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/permissions#activetab_permission\"><code>\"activeTab\"</code> permission</a>.</p>\n<p>Many tab operations use a Tab <code>id</code>. Tab <code>id</code>s are guaranteed to be unique to a single tab only within a browser session. If the browser is restarted, then it can and will reuse tab <code>id</code>s. To associate information with a tab across browser restarts, use <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/sessions/setTabValue\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">sessions.setTabValue() (en-US)</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"types","title":"Types","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.mutedinforeason\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/MutedInfoReason\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.MutedInfoReason (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the reason a tab was muted or unmuted.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.mutedinfo\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/MutedInfo\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.MutedInfo (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>This object contains a boolean indicating whether the tab is muted, and the reason for the last state change.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.pagesettings\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/PageSettings\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.PageSettings (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Used to control how a tab is rendered as a PDF by the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/saveAsPDF\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.saveAsPDF() (en-US)</a> method.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.tab\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/Tab\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.Tab (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>This type contains information about a tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.tabstatus\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/TabStatus\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.TabStatus (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Indicates whether the tab has finished loading.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.windowtype\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/WindowType\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.WindowType (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The type of window that hosts this tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.zoomsettingsmode\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/ZoomSettingsMode\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.ZoomSettingsMode (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Defines whether zoom changes are handled by the browser, by the extension, or are disabled.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.zoomsettingsscope\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/ZoomSettingsScope\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.ZoomSettingsScope (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Defines whether zoom changes will persist for the page's origin, or only take effect in this tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.zoomsettings\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/ZoomSettings\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.ZoomSettings (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Defines zoom settings <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/ZoomSettingsMode\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">mode (en-US)</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/ZoomSettingsScope\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">scope (en-US)</a>, and default zoom factor.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.tab_id_none\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/TAB_ID_NONE\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.TAB_ID_NONE (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A special ID value given to tabs that are not browser tabs (for example, tabs in devtools windows).</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"functions","title":"Functions","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.capturetab\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/captureTab\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.captureTab() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Creates a data URI encoding an image of the visible area of the given tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.capturevisibletab\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/captureVisibleTab\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.captureVisibleTab() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Creates a data URI encoding an image of the visible area of the currently active tab in the specified window.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.connect\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/connect\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.connect() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets up a messaging connection between the extension's background scripts (or other privileged scripts, such as popup scripts or options page scripts) and any <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Content_scripts\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">content scripts (en-US)</a> running in the specified tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.create\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/create\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.create() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Creates a new tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.detectlanguage\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/detectLanguage\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.detectLanguage() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Detects the primary language of the content in a tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.discard\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/discard\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.discard() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Discards one or more tabs.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.duplicate\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/duplicate\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.duplicate() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Duplicates a tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.executescript\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/executeScript\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.executeScript() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Injects JavaScript code into a page.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.get\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/get\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.get() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retrieves details about the specified tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.getallinwindow\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/getAllInWindow\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.getAllInWindow() (en-US)</a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Gets details about all tabs in the specified window.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.getcurrent\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/getCurrent\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.getCurrent() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Gets information about the tab that this script is running in, as a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/Tab\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.Tab (en-US)</a> object.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.getselected\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/getSelected\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.getSelected() (en-US)</a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Gets the tab that is selected in the specified window. <strong>Deprecated: use <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/query\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.query({active: true}) (en-US)</a> instead.</strong></p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.getzoom\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/getZoom\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.getZoom() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Gets the current zoom factor of the specified tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.getzoomsettings\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/getZoomSettings\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.getZoomSettings() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Gets the current zoom settings for the specified tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.goforward\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/goForward\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.goForward() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Go forward to the next page, if one is available.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.goback\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/goBack\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.goBack() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Go back to the previous page, if one is available.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.hide\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/hide\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.hide() (en-US)</a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Hides one or more tabs.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.highlight\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/highlight\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.highlight() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Highlights one or more tabs.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.insertcss\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/insertCSS\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.insertCSS() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Injects CSS into a page.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.move\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/move\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.move() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Moves one or more tabs to a new position in the same window or to a different window.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.moveinsuccession\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/moveInSuccession\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.moveInSuccession() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Modifies the succession relationship for a group of tabs.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.print\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/print\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.print() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Prints the contents of the active tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.printpreview\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/printPreview\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.printPreview() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Opens print preview for the active tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.query\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/query\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.query() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Gets all tabs that have the specified properties, or all tabs if no properties are specified.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.reload\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/reload\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.reload() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Reload a tab, optionally bypassing the local web cache.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.remove\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/remove\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.remove() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Closes one or more tabs.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.removecss\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/removeCSS\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.removeCSS() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Removes from a page CSS which was previously injected by calling <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/insertCSS\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.insertCSS() (en-US)</a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.saveaspdf\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/saveAsPDF\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.saveAsPDF() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Saves the current page as a PDF.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.sendmessage\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/sendMessage\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.sendMessage() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sends a single message to the content script(s) in the specified tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.sendrequest\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/sendRequest\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.sendRequest() (en-US)</a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sends a single request to the content script(s) in the specified tab. <strong>Deprecated</strong>: use <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/sendMessage\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.sendMessage() (en-US)</a> instead.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.setzoom\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/setZoom\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.setZoom() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Zooms the specified tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.setzoomsettings\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/setZoomSettings\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.setZoomSettings() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets the zoom settings for the specified tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.show\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/show\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.show() (en-US)</a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Shows one or more tabs that have been <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/hide\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">hidden (en-US)</a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.togglereadermode\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/toggleReaderMode\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.toggleReaderMode() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Toggles Reader mode for the specified tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.update\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/update\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.update() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Navigate the tab to a new URL, or modify other properties of the tab.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"events","title":"Events","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onactivated\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onActivated\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onActivated (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fires when the active tab in a window changes. Note that the tab's URL may not be set at the time this event fired.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onactivechanged\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onActiveChanged\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onActiveChanged (en-US)</a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fires when the selected tab in a window changes. <strong>Deprecated:</strong> use <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onActivated\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onActivated (en-US)</a> instead.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onattached\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onAttached\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onAttached (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fired when a tab is attached to a window, for example because it was moved between windows.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.oncreated\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onCreated\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onCreated (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fired when a tab is created. Note that the tab's URL may not be set at the time this event fired.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.ondetached\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onDetached\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onDetached (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fired when a tab is detached from a window, for example because it is being moved between windows.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onhighlightchanged\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onHighlightChanged\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onHighlightChanged (en-US)</a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fired when the highlighted or selected tabs in a window change. <strong>Deprecated:</strong> use <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onHighlighted\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onHighlighted (en-US)</a> instead.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onhighlighted\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onHighlighted\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onHighlighted (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fired when the highlighted or selected tabs in a window change.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onmoved\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onMoved\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onMoved (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fired when a tab is moved within a window.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onremoved\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onRemoved\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onRemoved (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fired when a tab is closed.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onreplaced\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onReplaced\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onReplaced (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fired when a tab is replaced with another tab due to prerendering.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onselectionchanged\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onSelectionChanged\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onSelectionChanged (en-US)</a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fires when the selected tab in a window changes. <strong>Deprecated:</strong> use <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onActivated\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onActivated (en-US)</a> instead.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onupdated\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onUpdated\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onUpdated (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fired when a tab is updated.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tabs.onzoomchange\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/onZoomChange\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabs.onZoomChange (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fired when a tab is zoomed.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"compatibilidade_com_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"webextensions.api.tabs","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_extensions","title":"Example extensions","isH3":false,"content":"<ul><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/annotate-page\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">annotate-page</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/apply-css\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">apply-css</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/beastify\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">beastify</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/bookmark-it\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bookmark-it</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/chill-out\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">chill-out</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/commands\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">commands</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/context-menu-copy-link-with-types\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">context-menu-copy-link-with-types</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/contextual-identities\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">contextual-identities</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/cookie-bg-picker\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">cookie-bg-picker</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/devtools-panels\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">devtools-panels</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/find-across-tabs\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">find-across-tabs</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/firefox-code-search\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">firefox-code-search</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/history-deleter\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">history-deleter</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/imagify\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">imagify</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/list-cookies\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">list-cookies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/menu-demo\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">menu-demo</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/menu-labelled-open\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">menu-labelled-open</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/menu-remove-element\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">menu-remove-element</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/open-my-page-button\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">open-my-page-button</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/permissions\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">permissions</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/session-state\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">session-state</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/store-collected-images\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">store-collected-images</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/tabs-tabs-tabs\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">tabs-tabs-tabs</a></li></ul>\n<blockquote>\n  <p><strong>Nota:</strong> <strong>Acknowledgements</strong>This API is based on Chromium's <a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/tabs\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>chrome.tabs</code></a> API. This documentation is derived from <a href=\"https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/src/+/master/chrome/common/extensions/api/tabs.json\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>tabs.json</code></a> in the Chromium code.Microsoft Edge compatibility data is supplied by Microsoft Corporation and is included here under the Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 United States License.</p>\n</blockquote>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Types","id":"types"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Functions","id":"functions"},{"text":"Events","id":"events"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"compatibilidade_com_navegadores"},{"text":"Example extensions","id":"example_extensions"}],"summary":"Interact with the browser's tab system.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"tabs","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"tabs","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"tabs","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"tabs","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"tabs","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"tabs","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/api/tabs","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/api/tabs/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla","title":"Mozilla"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons","title":"Complementos"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions","title":"Extensões do navegador"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API","title":"JavaScript APIs"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs","title":"tabs"}],"pageTitle":"tabs - Mozilla | MDN","noIndexing":false}}